  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_04_09: Rabbi Jonathan said: whoever fulfills the Torah out of a state of poverty, hi...",
  "body": "Rabbi Jonathan said: whoever fulfills the Torah out of a state of poverty, his end will be to fulfill it out of a state of wealth; And whoever discards the Torah out of a state of wealth, his end will be to discard it out of a state of poverty.",
